title: Labour Party leader Ababu Namwamba questions IEBC preparedness - VIDEO | The Standard
text:
Checkpoint / 10 hours ago [VIDEO] Labour Party leader Ababu Namwamba questions IEBC preparedness 
Labor party of Kenya is concerned over the anomalies in the ongoing voter registration exercise and says this casts doubts over its competence. Party leader Ababu Namwamba says it is worrying that the anomalies if not corrected can be a recipe for chaos after the general election. He was speaking in a Nakuru hotel after a two day retreat for officials of the party. Related Videos
